                            playing the piano ðŸŽ¹, cooking ðŸ¥©, discovering new
                            places ðŸ§³, and learning something new ðŸ“š.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Thanks for stopping by,<br />
                            &mdash; Andrei
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="sticky top-0 hidden h-screen lg:block" role="presentation">
            <Picture
                src={coverImage}
                formats={['avif', 'webp']}
                alt=""
                class="object-cover object-left-top h-screen"
            />
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
